                    "script": "\ttry:\n\t\timport json \n\t\tsearchTerm \u003d self.getSibling(\"TextField\").props.text\n\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\"starting search..\" + searchTerm)\n\t\tutils.messages.waiting.showLoading()\n\t\tif len(searchTerm) \u003e 3:\n\t\t\tdeviceList \u003d system.sitesync.searchDevice(searchTerm, self.session.custom.tenantID)\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(deviceList)\n\t\t\tresults \u003d []\n\t\t\tif deviceList !\u003d None or  deviceList !\u003d \"\":\n\t\t\t\tdList \u003d json.loads(deviceList)\n\t\t\t\tfor d in dList:\n\t\t\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(d)\n\t\t\t\t\tj \u003d {\n\t\t\t\t\t  \"instanceStyle\": {\n\t\t\t\t\t    \"classes\": \"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t  },\n\t\t\t\t\t  \"instancePosition\": {},\n\t\t\t\t\t  \"device\": d\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\tresults.append(j)\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\tself.parent.parent.getChild(\"searchQR\").props.instances \u003d results\n\t\t\tutils.messages.waiting.hideLoading()\n\t\telse:\n\t\t\tutils.messages.waiting.hideLoading()\n\t\t\tutils.messages.errors.showErrorMessage(\"Please enter at least 4 characters\")\n\texcept Exception as e:\n\t\tsystem.perspective.print(str(e))\n\t\tutils.messages.errors.showErrorMessage(\"Error searching: \" + str(e))"
