                  "script": "\t# implement your handler here\n\timport json\n\timport time\n\t\t\n\tlogger \u003d system.util.getLogger(\u0027SiteSyncQRSearch\u0027)\n\n\ttry:\n\t\tlogger.info(str(payload))\n\t\tscannedData \u003d payload[\u0027scanValue\u0027]\n\t\tresults \u003d utils.QRCodeParser.parse(scannedData)\n\t\tlogger.info(str(results))\n\t\n\t\tif results[\u0027devEUI\u0027] !\u003d \"\":\n\t\t\n\t\t\tfoundDevice \u003d system.sitesync.lookupDevice(results[\u0027devEUI\u0027])\n\t\t\tlogger.info(foundDevice)\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tutils.messages.waiting.hideLoading()\n\t\t\tif foundDevice !\u003d None:\n\t\t\t\tfoundDevice \u003d json.loads(foundDevice)\n\t\t\t\tsystem.perspective.navigate(page\u003d\"/devices/{0}\".format(results[\u0027devEUI\u0027]))\n\t\t\telse:\n\t\t\t\tutils.messages.errors.showErrorMessage(\"Device with EUI: \" + results[\u0027devEUI\u0027] + \" not found, try adding it first\")\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\telse:\n\t\t\tutils.messages.waiting.hideLoading()\n\t\t\tutils.messages.errors.showErrorMessage(\"DevEUI not found in scan: \" + scannedData)\n\t\t\ttime.sleep(2)\n\t\t\tutils.messages.errors.hideErrorMessage(\"\")\n\t\t\tlogger.info(\"No devEUI found: \" + scannedData)\n\texcept Exception as e:\n\t\tlogger.info(str(e))\n\t\tutils.messages.waiting.hideLoading()",
